  "We use cookies and similar technologies to ensure our theater events booking platform works properly, enhance your experience, and provide you with relevant information about upcoming shows. Strictly necessary cookies are always active as they are essential for the website to function. With your consent, we would also like to use analytics cookies to understand how visitors use our site and improve our services, as well as marketing cookies to personalize content and offers. In addition, you can choose to receive marketing emails and push notifications about new events, special promotions, and booking reminders. You can manage your preferences at any time. By clicking “Accept All,” you agree to the use of all cookies and communications. You may “Reject All” non-essential cookies and opt out of communications, or customize your settings below.": "我们使用cookie和类似技术，以确保我们的剧院活动预订平台正常运行，增强您的体验，并为您提供有关即将举行的演出的相关信息。严格必要的cookie始终处于活动状态，因为它们对于网站的功能至关重要。有了您的同意，我们还想使用分析cookie来了解访客如何使用我们的网站，并改进我们的服务，以及使用营销cookie来个性化内容和优惠。此外，您可以选择接收有关新活动、特别促销和预订提醒的营销电子邮件和推送通知。您可以随时管理您的偏好。通过点击“接受所有”，您同意使用所有cookie和通信。您可以“拒绝所有”非必需的cookie，并选择退出通信，或者自定义您的设置，如下所示。",
